Uncomplicated firewall
show description:
    apt show ufw
install:
    sudo apt install ufw

enable firewall (at startup)
    sudo ufw enable

check service status
    sudo servic ufw status

check ufw status
    sudo ufw status
    sudo ufw status numbered

ufw add rule
    sudo ufw allow <port number>
    sudo ufw delete <rule number> (use ufw status numbered to get the number)